<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ba67ca6b2292dc09a7fdf9cbb5126fcf>.
<#ba67ca6b2292dc09a7fdf9cbb5126fcf> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
