<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d6e6a60f34a80823664086b54e0223d0>.
<#d6e6a60f34a80823664086b54e0223d0> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U07526>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-16T06:38:21.771Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
