_:b0__4419 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((17.7605 59.4402,18.2011 59.4402,18.2011 59.2272,17.7605 59.2272,17.7605 59.4402))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
