    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Photogrammetric 3D model of the Vendel I helmet, an iron helmet with applied bronze decorations including remains of figure scenes of pressed sheet metal. The helmet was excavated from an Iron Age boat grave (Vendel I) in Vendel Parish, Uppsala County and is currently held in the collections of the National Historical Museums in Stockholm.\n\nLink to Sök I Samlingarna  \n\nhttps://samlingar.shm.se/object/F0DD41E6-54C5-41FC-9AE4-C865CD8FEB2F\n\nLink to the Dynamic Collection platform  \n\nhttps://dyncolldev.ht.lu.se/plus/artifact_view.php?item=847"@en;
