    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021003138>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This dataset contain data sources used in bibliometric studies. Every row corresponds to one data source so there will be multiple rows for articles containing multiple sources. The column norm_coarse corresponds to data source category and norm_fine to data source (only available for bibliographical metadata sources). See article for details.Related article: Lindelöw, C. H., Hammarfelt, B., & Mazoni, A. (2025). Data sources used in bibliometrics 1978–2022: From proprietary databases to the great wide open. Journal of the Association for Information Science and Technology, 1–14. https://doi.org/10.1002/asi.25018"@en;
