    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Developers Talking About Code Quality: study design and dataset"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__9838.
_:b0__9838 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/458d75b788f0ff871320b2b40ba51738>;
