}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#a8f0a8e459094ca6c1d44eddc97e2504>.
<#a8f0a8e459094ca6c1d44eddc97e2504> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N00334>;
